make build options:
OLDENGINE - SDL1.2 support
WITH_JSON - add json format
WITH_LUA - add lua support
WITH_DLL - add load shared libs support, with -ldl
WITH_XML - add tinyxml2 support
WITH_ICONV - usage iconv for Tools::stringEncode
DISABLE_NETWORK - disable SDL_net
DISABLE_AUDIO - disable SDL_mixer
DISABLE_IMAGE - disable SDL_image
DISABLE_TTF - disable SDL_ttf
BUILD_DEBUG_MESSAGES - DEBUG works
